To our amazing Elites & Leads, thank you for going on this journey with me and opening yourself up to this process. I know there were late nights, many ‚Äòagains‚Äô, so many 8-counts to learn (on video & in person), changes, me stressed, you stressed, all stressed, and time never being on our side; Through it all though I saw you push through these hardships and show your true colors in not only your love for dance, but love for putting in the work and for not settling for the bare minimum. I saw so many of you breakdown during this process and then gloriously breakthrough and triumph over these hurdles. I am so proud to have been just a small part of your journey and hope that you have learned lessons here that you take with you through your whole life.

Now go fly and show this world everything you got, you are all worthy of greatness. I love you always and  I am always here for you! ‚ù§Ô∏è
